		<div class="vatsonio-hero">
			<div class="vatsonio-overlay"></div>
			<div class="vatsonio-cover" data-stellar-background-ratio="0.5" style="background-image: url(images/home-blur-1.png);">
				<div class="desc animate-box">
					<div class="container">
						<div class="row">
							<div class="col-md-7">
								<h2><br> <b>Знайдіть допомогу, яка вам потрібна</b></h2>
								<p><span>Created with <i class="icon-heart3"></i> by <a href="https://twitter.com/vatsonio" class="vatsonio-site-name" onclick="document.getElementById('sound1').play();">Divass</a></span></p>
